=== 2019–present: Upcoming album ===
On February 4, 2019, Mahone released his new single "Why Don't We," which is penned by Charlie Puth and categorized as a fusion of modern pop and old school R&B under the 90s' influences.
The music video was released on March 2, 2019, on YouTube.
He has also photoed for the Galore Magazine on February 14, 2019, as the cover star to talk about his new music.
He also released a new single called "Summer Love", on October 16, 2020, and which he previewed through OnlyFans.
He briefly dated Cuban-American singer Camila Cabello in 2014.
The two split in February 2017.
